title: DuckTales OSTs
description:
Music from the well-loved DuckTales series.

For the TV Show, there is only the main theme and the outro.

The OST from the movie; I got this from a web source, and as far as I can tell the soundtrack was never actually sold, but nonetheless this is what I have.

And finally, the bulk of the download: the NES DuckTales OST as well as the OST from its remake, released just a week ago or so :) note that both of these are direct rips, courtesy of the fine folk at FFShrine (I did no work on anything here other than tagging). As of yet, the Remastered OST has yet to be released in any other format.

Enjoy! Hopefully, there will be an official album release for Remastered (and by extension the NES game) soon, but this should suffice in the meantime!
